{"tid":2516804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"掌摑30巴兼腳踢　天水圍跪地少女遭朋友欺凌　網民：真係壞過凱婷","createTime":"2021-05-05T01:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T07:22:40.000Z","uid":271829,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"826dde7fb2566e1410eacf36d844565ed00c6fd2","tid":2516804,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T01:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7ux9-nHLym9RHAhrhTrxV88hBVA=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5NT6C2VRJJD37KYSQZ4NKYYLDI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7ux9-nHLym9RHAhrhTrxV88hBVA%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5NT6C2VRJJD37KYSQZ4NKYYLDI.jpg&h=8fdb6dd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「藍精靈」踢低「豆腐姐」。網上片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Zh3J1uUMgmpS4s5Y20g4kWDGzA4=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PRHYR7WVZRFUNG7FUFHCEFQMLY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZh3J1uUMgmpS4s5Y20g4kWDGzA4%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPRHYR7WVZRFUNG7FUFHCEFQMLY.jpg&h=5a6d9bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「黑妹」亦多次向「豆腐姐」施襲。網上片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n天水圍發生童黨欺凌事件，一名十多歲少女，被另外兩名年齡相若少女多次掌摑及腳踢，另有一人圍觀，一人拍片。長逾6分鐘片段事後被放上社交網站，據熟知事件的讀者表示，當時為今年3月17日，位於天水圍天瑞邨附近。被欺凌者是「豆腐姐」，施襲者為「黑妹」及姓池的「藍精靈」，三人互相認識。警方表示正了解事件。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210505/V2NSTK2HLBERLBX7ZX25UJKWPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210505%2FV2NSTK2HLBERLBX7ZX25UJKWPY%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK2WzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=f29158cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210505%2FV2NSTK2HLBERLBX7ZX25UJKWPY%2F&h=c2b5a71f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210505/V2NSTK2HLBERLBX7ZX25UJKWPY/</a>"},{"pid":"b9c4d735db4bf6df47a43bb4068865d9f3ba8db2","tid":2516804,"uid":372525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"灰外套個個隻腳幾長 不過幼咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d3a6943d7ff33a40419f8c51bc704ec3b96d0f","tid":2516804,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b9c4d735db4bf6df47a43bb4068865d9f3ba8db2","tid":2516804,"uid":372525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"灰外套個個隻腳幾長 不過幼咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T01:51:19.000Z","msg":"三個隻腳都靚<br />\n俾人打呢啲下次等我黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7626e920504f70e9c6ed2c141029724dbc262f2b","tid":2516804,"uid":55941,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T01:58:04.000Z","msg":"之前有牛丸<br />\n而家豆腐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b869b891d43c3831d282c521314ea4a411eef9fb","tid":2516804,"uid":393145,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:07:40.000Z","msg":"豆腐姐 藍精靈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4608c31c298a47a96e3dc6b97ec5aa35771b47e5","tid":2516804,"uid":372525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2d3a6943d7ff33a40419f8c51bc704ec3b96d0f","tid":2516804,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b9c4d735db4bf6df47a43bb4068865d9f3ba8db2","tid":2516804,"uid":372525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"灰外套個個隻腳幾長 不過幼咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c